  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink242-kilavi">talaimakaḷ aṟattoṭu nilai nayappa vēṇṭit tōḻi avaṭkuc colliyatu.   </p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> 
          What the confidante told the heroine, desiring that she yield to standing firm in duty (i.e., revealing the love affair to her mother).
          
          
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink242">
<l>aṟiyā maiyiṉ veṟiyeṉa mayaṅki</l>
<l>yaṉṉaiyu maruntuya ruḻantaṉa ḷataṉā</l>
<l>leyyātu viṭutalō koṭitē niraiyita</l>
<l>ḻāymala ruṇkaṇ pacappac</l>
<l>cēymalai nāṭaṉ ceyta nōyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>Out of ignorance, becoming confused and saying, “Veṟi-dance,”</l>
        <l>mother too suffered grievous misery. Therefore,</l>
        <l>letting [her] go, not knowing</l>
        <l>of the pain caused by the man from the distant mountain land,</l>
        <l>as her kohl[-lined] eyes, like beautiful blossoms with petals in rows, grow pale—</l>
        <l>would indeed be cruel.</l>
        
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
